name: strab
description:
Remember strub? Neither do I. But looking back (and examining the work with fresh eyes) it was something both organic and orgiastic. I won’t apologize for any of that. On the contrary, I did really enjoy making strub! Same goes for this one, called strab, which is a companion piece of sorts. It’s an improvement over strub in that there are 47 frames in strab and only 46 in strub.
